text: Nicole Vaidi코ov치 (born 23 April 1989 in Nuremberg) is a Czech professional female tennis player. She became a tennis professional in 2003, and debuted in several ITF tournaments. She measures at and weighs . She enjoys reading, watching movies, yoga, and bike riding. Her favorite city is New York City.
